  98:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****          (++) Configure these ADC pins in analog mode
  99:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****               using function HAL_GPIO_Init()
