 101:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****     (#) Optionally, in case of usage of ADC with interruptions:
 102:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****          (++) Configure the NVIC for ADC
