 110:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****               using function HAL_DMA_Init().
 111:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****          (++) Configure the NVIC for DMA
