 155:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****           (+++) Activate the ADC peripheral and start conversions
 156:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc.c ****                 using function HAL_ADC_Start_IT()
