 502:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         conditioned to ADC state.
 503:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   */
