5089:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - sequencer ranks
5090:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         This function is intended to be used when contexts queue is enabled,
