5835:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  AWDy This parameter can be one of the following values:
5836:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_AWD1
